\title{Complex exponential}
\author{alex-nelson}
\import{notation}
\date{2025-12-09}
\taxon{definition}
\meta{source}{[[lankham-2016-linear]] Section 2.3.4}

\p{Let #{z=x+\I y} be a complex number with #{x,y\in\RR}. Then we define the \define{Complex Exponential} to be a function #{\exp\colon\CC\to\CC} defined by
##{\exp(z)=\E^{x}\E^{\I y}=\E^{x}(\cos(y)+\I\sin(y))}}